title: How legitimate are CFP ranked teams?
description:
Trevor Matich, Sam Acho, and Wendi Nix break down the key components of success for Alabama and Michigan State this season. Todd McShay also joins the show to discuss his top WR prospects for the 2022 NFL Draft.
